Zen <p>Zenknight Darkhorse,
52 Champion,
Warlord ,
Screaming Fist</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubamilbanebringer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bamil Banebringer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/8/01 1:55:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=140.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EXP Groups</span><hr size=1> Had a nice all SG group in Karnors, was nice and relaxing... which usually isn't the case in that god forsaken place.<br>
