<b>~Amnesty, Saryrn~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubayen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bayen</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/11/01 6:16:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=140.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EXP Groups</span><hr size=1> Bayen is parked in DL at the karnor's castle wall and my necro who mostly solo's is in OT by the outpost at 16 i am about a bub of blue from dinging to 17 so anyone willing to make the trip come on by i will group with you lower levels for some real good xp in OT and will make the run to most anywhere for the good xp with bayen and my necro's name is zordain. <p><font size=4 color=purple>B<font size=3>ayen <font size=4>S<font size=3>kullsmasher<br>Warlord of the Screaming Fist<br>40th Season Human Paladin<br>Awful Smith<br> Feeble Potterer<br>Master Fletcher<br>Poor Brewer<br>Eastern Standard Time<br><br><br><br></font></font></font></font></font></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulandyalexandre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LandyAlexandre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/11/01 8:23:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=140.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EXP Groups</span><hr size=1> Just a thought, but i would be more than happy to duo with any 43+ tank for great exp at some point in the next few days.  My preferred loc is the